{"tid":2355373,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"記唔記得上年616、812、11月大三罷點嚟？","createTime":"2021-01-06T05:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T13:53:06.000Z","uid":80329,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d6589763063b917de9eb99f896a422fbf78cb6","tid":2355373,"uid":80329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">記唔記得上年616二百萬人遊行、812機場黑警還眼、11月大三罷點嚟？</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">直接導火線可以話係<span class=\"x-large\">615梁義士死諫</span>、<span class=\"x-large\">811女仔眼中槍</span>、同<span class=\"x-large\">11月8梓樂嘅死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋上年係同聲同氣，一方有難百方支援<br />\n<br />\n因為我哋唔只係共同體，重深明今日有人被咬唔出嚟，他日到你自己被咬已經冇人可以為你出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"maroon\">琴日外賣仔手足可以被咬<br />\n今日至少55個民主派人士不論光譜一律被狗咬晒，而且其實投票嘅60萬人都可以被捕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">佢哋被捕就被捕咗，問題係我哋重有冇勇氣企出嚟、有冇勇氣唔再吞聲忍氣、有冇勇氣講真話</span><br />\n<br />\n今次一定要企出嚟"},{"pid":"1264b3265b27f05c3d109c353209d438224142ed","tid":2355373,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449c46fc5e38c2706989c725968ec697b8b4b291","tid":2355373,"uid":18313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:34:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d739505e5f7ffb612a2dfe647d4c402f18aedf2","tid":2355373,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"咪撚再畀有疫情做唔出既藉口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}